{"tid":771032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大家鎮定啲］支國消息人士：人民銀行要求銀行防範人民幣市場羊群效應","createTime":"2018-08-07T14:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T01:22:46.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dd50ae18fea5c2ccef4aa3eb9db91261e80d809d","tid":771032,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒引述消息人士報道，人民銀行要求銀行防範人民幣市場羊群效應，又表示有信心維持人民幣穩定。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士說，人行本周一早上召集14家人民幣中間價報價銀行會談。有關主管官員在會議上表示，央行有信心、有豐富的政策工具來維護市場穩定，與會銀行應該與央行一起出力，防範羊群效應和順周期行為，對順周期行為不要推波助瀾。<br />\n<br />\n有關官員說，人民幣自6月以來有一定貶值，但跨境資金流動總體平衡，基本面因素支持人民幣匯率基本穩定。<br />\n<br />\n官員同時表示，考慮到未來存在不確定性，要保持匯率彈性、雙向浮動的導向不變，及時釋放壓力，避免與市場形成強對峙。與會銀行建議，可適時啟用逆周期因子等加強對匯率中間價的指導，並加強對境外市場監控，必要時可運用一些工具。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1411150-20180807.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1411150-20180807.htm&d=yGo76tklT05MsZmyErET3DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=adc6589a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1411150-20180807.htm&h=9f29db75\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1411150-20180807.htm</a>"},{"pid":"19d606c99c242dbcc2b911dd48c35fd0c72183f1","tid":771032,"uid":27206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T17:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4885078a527d8f6c145e2d941e37d6f2f913e5d","tid":771032,"uid":470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T18:00:13.000Z","msg":"順下行周期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287128dfe9a717ec3dc06fad3bd215e1b6d5d89f","tid":771032,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T18:07:42.000Z","msg":"山乳欲來"},{"pid":"9b99cfb2ab28775babe6c111329c261a0a21a82c","tid":771032,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":